{"tid":982172,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"有情又有義 KUBA貼錢返母會救亡","createTime":"2019-01-15T01:50:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-15T12:03:41.000Z","uid":35192,"like":26,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"4982f6b503e8ed98decf062b51efb4f5d6c68785","tid":982172,"uid":35192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T01:50:04.000Z","msg":"談到波蘭球星巴拉斯塞高斯基（KUBA），球迷們當然會記得他「水蛇春咁長」的名字，還有他童年悲慘的遭遇。原來KUBA已經與德甲禾夫斯堡解約，並將在今月回歸母會克拉科夫，他不收一分一毫之餘，更自掏腰包倒貼30萬鎊（約300萬港元），為的只是要助母會脫困。<br />\n<br />\n       事緣波蘭甲組聯賽班霸克拉科夫陷入財困，克拉科夫背後的柬埔寨財團未能在上月28日的限期前償還債務，最終要KUBA出手搶救。根外國傳媒報道，KUBA以免費形式加盟克拉科夫，他提供的30萬鎊會用來支付職球員的薪金，以及應付日常開支，直到有財團願意接手。<br />\n<br />\n        KUBA在2007年由克拉科夫轉至多蒙特，留效9季之後轉投禾夫斯堡，至月初與禾堡達成共識，解約並以自由身離隊。KUBA如此有情有義，多蒙特亦有在twitter發文讚揚他"},{"pid":"5756ae51732052595a1105a2dd1bce4388daa219","tid":982172,"uid":77355,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T01:52:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 義士"},{"pid":"6cc1a6dffb614a5ef44635887e33bb761854e54f","tid":982172,"uid":12169,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T01:54:08.000Z","msg":"真唔收錢踢波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88dffea12cbd0068640c0407025f4e38c0d971d2","tid":982172,"uid":70013,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"6cc1a6dffb614a5ef44635887e33bb761854e54f","tid":982172,"uid":12169,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T01:54:08.000Z","msg":"真唔收錢踢波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T02:02:35.000Z","msg":"大十字真正全能到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f1e6b9c945b0a962d78e917222aadb476a9326b","tid":982172,"uid":12169,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"88dffea12cbd0068640c0407025f4e38c0d971d2","tid":982172,"uid":70013,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"6cc1a6dffb614a5ef44635887e33bb761854e54f","tid":982172,"